instructions: Put the dinner fork on the left side of the table cloth
Place a dinner knife on the right side of the table cloth
Place a salad fork to the left of the dinner fork
Place the soup spoon on the table cloth
Place a soup spoon on the top of the table cloth
Put the dessert spoon on the right of the soup spoon on the table cloth
Move the dessert spoon horizontal on the top of the table cloth
Place the dinner plate in the center of the table cloth
Add a bread plate to the left of the dessert spoon
Place a butter knife on top of the bread plate
Place a wine glass above the soup spoon
Place a water glass to the left of the wine glass
Place a napkin on top of the dinner plate
